sence of the #6FrameStoryChallenge was to tell a good story using just 6 illustrations.\nThe campaign inspired nearly 70 illustrators to donate their time and skills to India’s first open-source story-publishing platform for children.\nWhat started out as an experimental campaign soon blossomed into a carnival of art, birthing nearly 500 new illustrations.\nThese wordless narratives cut across language barriers, opening up a world of possibilities, encouraging StoryWeaver’s growing community to dream up multiple stories around these images. The #6FrameStoryChallenge is a powerful reminder of the need for collaboration, to get closer to our mission: “A Book in Every Child’s Hand.”","words":[[195,"#6FrameStoryChallenge:"],[196,"A"],[197,"Carnival"],[198,"of"],[199,"Art"],[200,"The"],[201,"illustrations"],[202,"in"],[203,"this"],[204,"book"],[205,"were"],[206,"created"],[207,"as"],[208,"part"],[209,"of"],[210,"the"],[211,"#6FrameStoryChallenge,"],[212,"an"],[213,"online"],[214,"campaign"],[215,"run"],[216,"by"],[217,"Pratham"],[218,"Books"],[219,"to"],[220,"build"],[221,"a"],[222,"rich"],[223,"bank"],[224,"of"],[225,"illustrations"],[226,"for"],[227,"StoryWeaver."],[228,"The"],[229,"essence"],[230,"of"],[231,"the"],[232,"#6FrameStoryChallenge"],[233,"was"],[234,"to"],[235,"tell"],[236,"a"],[237,"good"],[238,"story"],[239,"using"],[240,"just"],[241,"6"],[242,"illustrations."],[243,"The"],[244,"campaign"],[245,"inspired"],[246,"nearly"],[247,"70"],[248,"illustrators"],[249,"to"],[250,"donate"],[251,"their"],[252,"time"],[253,"and"],[254,"skills"],[255,"to"],[256,"India’s"],[257,"first"],[258,"open-source"],[259,"story-publishing"],[260,"platform"],[261,"for"],[262,"children."],[263,"What"],[264,"started"],[265,"out"],[266,"as"],[267,"an"],[268,"experimental"],[269,"campaign"],[270,"soon"],[271,"blossomed"],[272,"into"],[273,"a"],[274,"carnival"],[275,"of"],[276,"art,"],[277,"birthing"],[278,"nearly"],[279,"500"],[280,"new"],[281,"illustrations."],[282,"These"],[283,"word